    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Hallucinatory Instrument</p><hr /><p>When you cast a genjutsu with the auditory keyword that deals damage using your Hallucinatory Instrument, you can force all targets to make a Wisdom saving throw against your genjutsu save DC, gaining 1 rank of fear on a failed save. A creature can remake this saving throw at the end of each of their turns if they can no longer hear you.</p>",
