      "description": "<p><strong>Max Ranks:</strong> 5 Creatures who would gain ranks of <strong>Fear (or Frightened)</strong>, gain ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong>.</p><p>• A <strong>Demoralized</strong> creature suffers a -1 penalty to its saving throws, for each rank they have.</p><p>• A <strong>Demoralized</strong> creature must make concentration checks at the beginning of each of their turns to maintain concentration on their jutsu.</p><p>• At the end of a <strong>Demoralized</strong> creatures turn they make a DC 13 Charisma ability check. On a success, they remove 1 rank of <strong>Demoralized</strong>. After 10 minutes, a creature who still has ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong>, loses all ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong> it has remaining</p><p>• As an action, a <strong>Demoralized</strong> creature can make a DC 20 Charisma ability check to remove all ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong> it has.</p>",
